---
layout: base-lite.njk
title: "Blog — Magalie Chetrit"
description: "Articles on web development, WordPress, JavaScript, and the tools I use."
permalink: /blog/index.html
---

<h1>Blog</h1>
<p>Writing on web development, WordPress, JavaScript, and the tools I use.</p>

<ul class="lite-post-list">
{%- for post in collections.post | sortByDateCreated -%}
    <li>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="excerpt">{{ post.data.description | safe }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <time datetime="{{ post.data.dateCreated }}">{{ post.data.dateCreated | makeDateReadable }}</time>
    </li>
{%- endfor -%}
</ul>
